"23:87:5" : {s: 23, a: 87, w: 5, r: "وقي", t: "تَتَّقُونَ", l: "ٱتَّقَىٰ", lc: 166, tl: "tattaqūna", lb: "কোনো কিছুর ব্যাপারে অত্যন্ত সচেতন থাকা, আল্লাহর প্রতি সচেতন থাকা",e: "you fear (Him)", b: "বেঁচে থাকতে পার (পাপ হতে)", i: "kamu bertakwa", f: 19, rm: "to protect, save, preserve, ward off, guard against evil and calamity, be secure, take as a shield, regard the duty. muttaqii - one who guard against evil and against that which harms and injures and is regardful of his duty towards human beings and God."},
